data.description: If you are looking character and charm then look no further!!! The home owners have added so much love and character that you have to see it to believe it. This is a (3) bedroom, (3) bath home with a large bonus area and a sunroom. Owners suite has barn doors and a large shower. The sunroom has been used as a cozy home for the fur babies to eat, rest and relax! Every section has been converted into a usable space. The closet next to the stairs is a functionable pantry. In the backyard is a storage building that will convey. Use your imagination and convert the raised garden bed into a play area with a sandbox! The home is in a desired school district and located conveniently to everything. And guess what??? Target is coming soon!!! A new roof, fresh paint, and new carpeting are coming! Did I mention a home warranty is being offered as well? What else do you need? Call me for a private showing.
